PrecisRe-appointment of JEAN-PIERRE BEAUQUIER, of Pointe-Claire, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and designation of JEAN-PIERRE BEAUQUIER as a coordinating member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office) for a term of two years; effective April 28, 2000.
